    <p>
      Whether you're a prospective sponsor, a student interested in joining, or simply curious about our work, drop us a line!
    </p>
    <div class="contact-block">
      <h3>A Little More About Us ...</h3>
      <p>
        Stony Brook Motorsports is a student-run team in the Baja SAE series. We design, build, and race open-wheel off-road vehicles from the ground up, mastering mechanical, electrical, and software engineeringâ€”plus business, logistics, and teamwork.
